<article class="config-card">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div>
      <p class="panel-kicker">IA e midia</p>
      <h3>Resumos e miniaturas do acervo</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="config-actions">
      <button id="enrichmentSave" type="button">Salvar configuracoes</button>
      <button id="enrichmentLoadModels" type="button">Carregar modelos</button>
      <button id="enrichmentRun" class="primary-button" type="button">Iniciar fila</button>
      <button id="enrichmentStop" class="ghost-button danger-button" type="button">Parar fila</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="stats-grid" id="enrichmentStats"></div>
  <div class="stats-grid">
    <article class="overview-stat"><span>Status</span><strong id="enrichmentStatusMode">Parado</strong></article>
    <article class="overview-stat"><span>Processados</span><strong id="enrichmentProcessedTotal">0</strong></article>
    <article class="overview-stat"><span>Erros</span><strong id="enrichmentErrorTotal">0</strong></article>
    <article class="overview-stat"><span>Media por item</span><strong id="enrichmentAvgTime">--</strong></article>
    <article class="overview-stat"><span>Gargalo</span><strong id="enrichmentBottleneckStage">--</strong></article>
    <article class="overview-stat"><span>Ultimo item</span><strong id="enrichmentLastItemTime">--</strong></article>
  </div>

  <div class="form-grid">
    <label>
      <span>Provider</span>
      <select id="enrichmentProvider">
        <option value="disabled">Desativado</option>
        <option value="local">IA local</option>
        <option value="cloud">API em nuvem</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Modelo</span>
      <input id="enrichmentModel" type="text" list="enrichmentModelOptions" placeholder="ex: qwen2.5, llama3.1, gpt-4o-mini" />
      <datalist id="enrichmentModelOptions"></datalist>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Base URL</span>
      <input id="enrichmentBaseUrl" type="text" placeholder="http://127.0.0.1:11434/v1 ou https://api..." />
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>API key</span>
      <input id="enrichmentApiKey" type="text" placeholder="Opcional para IA local" />
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Lote por execucao</span>
      <select id="enrichmentBatchLimit">
        <option value="3">3</option>
        <option value="5" selected>5</option>
        <option value="10">10</option>
        <option value="20">20</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Modo do processo</span>
      <select id="enrichmentProcessMode">
        <option value="both" selected>Resumo e miniaturas</option>
        <option value="summary_only">Somente resumo</option>
        <option value="images_only">Somente miniaturas</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Miniaturas por documento</span>
      <select id="enrichmentPreviewImageCount">
        <option value="1" selected>1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
        <option value="4">4</option>
        <option value="5">5</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Qualidade das imagens</span>
      <select id="enrichmentPreviewImageQuality">
        <option value="low">Baixa</option>
        <option value="balanced" selected>Balanceada</option>
        <option value="high">Alta</option>
      </select>
    </label>
  </div>

  <div class="button-row">
    <label class="toggle-line strong-line">
      <input id="enrichmentSummaryEnabled" type="checkbox" checked />
      <span>Gerar resumos trabalhados para os documentos</span>
    </label>
    <label class="toggle-line strong-line">
      <input id="enrichmentPreviewImagesEnabled" type="checkbox" />
      <span>Gerar miniaturas leves da primeira pagina</span>
    </label>
    <label class="toggle-line strong-line">
      <input id="enrichmentOverwriteSummary" type="checkbox" />
      <span>Refazer resumos mesmo quando o documento ja tiver resumo</span>
    </label>
    <label class="toggle-line strong-line">
      <input id="enrichmentOverwritePreviewImages" type="checkbox" />
      <span>Refazer miniaturas mesmo quando o documento ja tiver imagens</span>
    </label>
  </div>

  <p class="config-note">
    Defina se a fila deve trabalhar com resumo, miniaturas ou ambos. As miniaturas sao gravadas em <strong>`data/media/previews`</strong>, e as imagens adicionais tambem entram na galeria do documento.
  </p>
  <div class="config-section-grid compact-grid">
    <div>
      <h4 class="config-subtitle">Documento em enriquecimento</h4>
      <div id="enrichmentCurrentItem" class="stack-list"></div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="config-subtitle">Ultimo enriquecido</h4>
      <div id="enrichmentLastItemCard" class="stack-list"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="config-note" id="enrichmentFeedback">Aguardando configuracao.</p>
  <div id="enrichmentResults" class="stack-list"></div>
</article>
